{"tid":849014,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【跟肥媽大灣區食鯇魚魚生】強調唔係跟稿讀 黃美琪：食完精神爽利","createTime":"2018-10-05T11:15:33.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-05T14:27:23.000Z","uid":78546,"like":18,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"5984c080aef4a48d8ea31db11397156e70bbf035","tid":849014,"uid":78546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-05T11:15:33.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20181005&amp;s=7018882&amp;a=58759955\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20181005%26s%3D7018882%26a%3D58759955&d=dzHijIxb1BJdM2dR2xKuSf755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=0281e1fb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20181005%26s%3D7018882%26a%3D58759955&h=588facaf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20181005&amp;s=7018882&amp;a=58759955</a> <br />\n本港食安中心及衞生署衞生防護中心先後在facebook發帖，直指最近有電視節目介紹用鯇魚製作魚生，引起關注，強調「切勿進食淡水魚生」。而肥媽Maria Cordero主持嘅《大灣區 活好D》，節目上有份食鯇魚魚生嘅黃美琪大讚冇血味同腥味，好好食。<br />\n<br />\n不過，食安中心都呼籲切勿進食淡水魚生，有可能帶有致病菌或寄生蟲，美琪BB今日接受傳媒訪問時話未睇新聞，佢話：「都唔係好擔心嘅......聽講係自己養殖(鯇魚)，當日間餐廳同師傅都好專業，做開切魚生嘅，所以好放心食，冇考慮呢樣嘢。」<br />\n<br />\n美琪BB透露食後感唔係照稿讀，係發自內心，佢話﹕「係食完自己講感受，真心覺得幾好食，原來可以咁食，我係抱住好奇心態去試，食完都精神爽利。」美琪直言自己健康一向唔太差，但都呼籲腸胃唔好嘅人要小心選擇，佢話﹕「咁一向都話三文魚有蟲，但自己都鍾意食，有時在難免，咁當然腸胃唔好都要自己選擇。」<br />\n<br />\n節目中（第七集）一開始，肥媽就問兩位主持：黃美琪同林伊麗，問佢哋覺得佛山點啦，然後話題一扯就扯到去大灣區，肥媽仲話：「大灣區呢，我覺得有啲嘢，佢哋係比香港仲先進。」例如呢？街市「電子化」已超越香港&mdash;&mdash;「你傻嘅咩，依家邊有人帶錢出嚟買餸0架？用電話0架嘛！」"},{"pid":"9f0d366e352e64917c1d8a9ee296fd3b3c876ff4","tid":849014,"uid":56462,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-05T11:19:10.000Z","msg":"想嘔<br />\n屌佢老母"},{"pid":"718264869a2d201a3cc2a41f64cd57b98e100765","tid":849014,"uid":116289,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-05T11:19:51.000Z","msg":"蝗美琪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad981a0853755f5b8148904ac6dcf857d5f3bc7c","tid":849014,"uid":34023,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-05T11:26:49.000Z","msg":"屌你快撚到<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">即刻駁咀<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span>"},{"pid":"cf620c3de0d40fbe0aeed963473746ff0b7eccfa","tid":849014,"uid":15815,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-05T11:26:58.000Z","msg":"屎都食得<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"821f37ea8463022ec70b467df75d1f2cafc2e968","tid":849014,"uid":99700,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-05T13:23:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://i1.go2yd.com/image.php?url=0IyggUQQew\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi1.go2yd.com%2Fimage.php%3Furl%3D0IyggUQQew&h=9a147db8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a36d7157709ad899a67cdd9ed1f83c901380c1b2","tid":849014,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-05T13:24:18.000Z","msg":"維基竟然未UPDATE<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/黃美棋\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%E9%BB%83%E7%BE%8E%E6%A3%8B&d=dzHijIxb1BJdM2dR2xKuSf755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=73d3b023\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/黃美棋</a>"},{"pid":"efe2f1f759b4fe3e23beac651982dfb091927e5a","tid":849014,"uid":79563,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-05T13:25:00.000Z","msg":"UC Berkeley都咁白痴"},{"pid":"a53e774aee650b70cf55f2cec35e70fa09a23533","tid":849014,"uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"cf620c3de0d40fbe0aeed963473746ff0b7eccfa","tid":849014,"uid":15815,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-05T11:26:58.000Z","msg":"屎都食得<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-05T13:25:10.000Z","msg":"UC Berkeley都咁白痴"},{"pid":"6bc57be175ab35453a47e6453887e3721ba77e47","tid":849014,"